<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q54_v1" title="Q54_v1" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En una encuesta a 50 estudiantes sobre su género musical preferido se obtuvieron los siguientes resultados: 14 prefirieron pop, 11 rock, 9 reggaetón, 8 baladas y 8 música clásica.</p>
    <div>
      Si se elige al azar a uno de estos estudiantes, ¿qué fracción del curso prefiere pop o baladas como su género musical preferido?
    </div>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Elige la alternativa que corresponde a esa fracción.</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>7</m:mn>
            <m:mn>25</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Los estudiantes que prefieren pop o baladas son <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> de un total de <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math>, por lo que la fracción es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Al simplificar, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> se convierte en <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, no en <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>11</m:mn>
            <m:mn>25</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Los estudiantes que prefieren pop o baladas son <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> de un total de <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math>, así que la fracción es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Simplificando por <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:mn>25</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La cantidad que prefiere pop o baladas es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo tanto la fracción buscada es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> y no <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. De hecho, <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> equivale a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, que representa solo a 8 de 50 estudiantes.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>11</m:mn>
            <m:mn>50</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La suma correcta es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que la fracción es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Al simplificar, resulta <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. La opción <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> es la mitad de <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, por eso no corresponde a la fracción pedida.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar los géneros que pide el problema</strong></p>
            <p>Se pide la fracción de estudiantes que prefieren pop o baladas.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Sumar las cantidades correspondientes</strong></p>
            <p>Prefieren pop: <m:math><m:mn>14</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Prefieren baladas: <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Hay <m:math><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math> estudiantes que prefieren pop o baladas.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Escribir la fracción sobre el total del curso</strong></p>
            <p>El total de estudiantes es <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La fracción es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Simplificar la fracción</strong></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math> son divisibles por <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, se obtiene:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> <m:math><m:mo>=</m:mo></m:math> <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La fracción del curso que prefiere pop o baladas como su género musical preferido es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mn>25</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>